  "summary": "What's Changed Simplify Android build: bundletool + eas submit by @mozzius in #9855 Add nightly iOS/Android build workflow by @estrattonbailey in #10940 Bump version to 1.126.0 by @estrattonbailey in #10942 Fix nightly build workflow by @estrattonbailey in #10943 Restore ALT badges in quoted posts by @jcsalterego in #10964 Process videos on web with WebCode…",
  "content": "<h2>What&#x27;s Changed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Simplify Android build: bundletool + eas submit by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/9855\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#9855</a></li>\n<li>Add nightly iOS/Android build workflow by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10940\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10940</a></li>\n<li>Bump version to 1.126.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10942\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10942</a></li>\n<li>Fix nightly build workflow by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10943\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10943</a></li>\n<li>Restore ALT badges in quoted posts by <a href=\"https://github.com/jcsalterego\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@jcsalterego</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10964\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10964</a></li>\n<li>Process videos on web with WebCodecs by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10955\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10955</a></li>\n<li>bskyweb: add isPartOf jsonld post attr by <a href=\"https://github.com/blackmichael\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@blackmichael</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10945\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10945</a></li>\n<li>Add TestFlight group selection to iOS build workflow by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10979\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10979</a></li>\n<li>Add mark all as read to chat settings by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10973\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10973</a></li>\n<li>Fix embeds overlapping each other in chat by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10949\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10949</a></li>\n<li>Remove old message composer by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10951\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10951</a></li>\n<li>Add light haptics to Edit Profile Button for labellers by <a href=\"https://github.com/RetroSunstar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@RetroSunstar</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10948\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10948</a></li>\n<li>Fix setState-in-render warning from convo cache subscription by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10934\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10934</a></li>\n<li>Fix internal repo sync broken by actions/checkout v6 bump by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10933\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10933</a></li>\n<li>Tweak strings and context by <a href=\"https://github.com/surfdude29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@surfdude29</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10928\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10928</a></li>\n<li>Set a min height on native Menus by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10956\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10956</a></li>\n<li>signup: align &quot;Contact support&quot; to the right on larger displays by <a href=\"https://github.com/iLynxcat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@iLynxcat</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10978\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10978</a></li>\n<li>[APP-2429] Add Sunlight and Twilight color options to the Invite Friends QR code by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10921\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10921</a></li>\n<li>Fix issue with stale unread message counts by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10953\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10953</a></li>\n<li>Focus composer input when editable by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10982\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10982</a></li>\n<li>Upgrade pnpm to 11.9.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10952\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10952</a></li>\n<li>Add new chat notification preferences by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10972\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10972</a></li>\n<li>Display more information in chat replies by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10950\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10950</a></li>\n<li>Video alt text by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10990\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10990</a></li>\n<li>Show shorter text for account label badge by <a href=\"https://github.com/abenzer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@abenzer</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10983\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10983</a></li>\n<li>Add icon to AppLanguageDropdown by <a href=\"https://github.com/iLynxcat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@iLynxcat</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10977\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10977</a></li>\n<li>Increase unread cap to 99+ by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10985\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10985</a></li>\n<li>Hide autocomplete suggestions when input loses focus by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10989\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10989</a></li>\n<li>Add video upload telemetry events by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10991\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10991</a></li>\n<li>Add placeholder, empty-value, and onConfirm support to DateField by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10993\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10993</a></li>\n<li>Change dialog label and header from &#x27;Invite Friends&#x27; to &#x27;Share Profile&#x27; by <a href=\"https://github.com/gabecodez\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@gabecodez</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10987\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10987</a></li>\n<li>Bump actions/download-artifact from 7.0.0 to 8.0.1 by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10971\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10971</a></li>\n<li>Clean up type/lint errors in <code>modules</code> by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10996\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10996</a></li>\n<li>Add app language: Czech (<code>cs</code>) by <a href=\"https://github.com/surfdude29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@surfdude29</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10994\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10994</a></li>\n<li>Fail video duration check before compression by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10999\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10999</a></li>\n<li>Add advanced search UI by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10992\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10992</a></li>\n<li>Fix GrowthBook exposure did mis-attribution across account switches by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11000</a></li>\n<li>Fix 149/150 user limit for starter packs by <a href=\"https://github.com/RetroSunstar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@RetroSunstar</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11001\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11001</a></li>\n<li>Set apple team id via environment variable by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11008\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11008</a></li>\n<li>Fix CI - grant workflows permission for internal sync push by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11010\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11010</a></li>\n<li>Disable selectable profile description on Android by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11002\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11002</a></li>\n<li>Fix chat input positioning on mobile android by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11013\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11013</a></li>\n<li>Release Prep 1.126.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11015\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11015</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>New Contributors</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/iLynxcat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@iLynxcat</a> made their first contribution in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10978\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10978</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/gabecodez\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@gabecodez</a> made their first contribution in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10987\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10987</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Full Changelog</strong>: <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/compare/1.125.0...1.126.0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1.125.0...1.126.0</a></p>",
